Package: spagmix
Type: Package
Title: Artificial Spatial and Spatiotemporal Densities on Bounded
        Windows
Version: 0.3-4
Date: 2021-02-16
Author: Anna K. Redmond and Tilman M. Davies
Maintainer: Tilman M. Davies <tilman.davies@otago.ac.nz>
Description: A utility package containing some simple tools to design and generate density functions on bounded regions in space and space-time, and simulate iid data therefrom. See Davies & Lawson (2019) <doi:10.1080/00949655.2019.1575066> for example.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), spatstat.geom, spatstat.core, spatstat.linnet,
        spatstat (>= 2.0-0)
Imports: RandomFields, abind, sparr, mvtnorm
Suggests: rgl
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation: no
Packaged: 2021-03-14 20:31:28 UTC; tilmandavies
Repository: CRAN
Date/Publication: 2021-03-15 00:00:03 UTC
